title: Great Bend United Futbol Club
text:
Great Bend United Futbol Club POSTED October 21, 2015 11:20 a.m. / 1 2 
COURTESY PHOTOSThe Under 14 and Under 12 Great Bend United Futbol Club teams participated in the Mid Kansas Cup tournament this past weekend in Salina. Both teams finished 3-0-0 bringing home the trophies in their divisions. The U14 team pictured includes: Back row: assistant coach Jesus Loera Luis Zamarripa, Jesus Sanchez, Rogelio Arias, Humberto Alonso, Eduardo Villalobos and coach Israel Franco; middle row, Daniel Cervantes, Simon Hernandez, Eric Ibarra and Francisco Garcia; and front row: Armando Leyva, Israel Franco Jr, Oscar Martinez and Rodrigo Ordonez. The U12 team pictured includes: Back row: Juan Garcia, Carlos Batres, Angel Razo, Jonathan Pasos, Brian Cervantes, Axel Leyva and Juan Sanchez; and front row: Luis Manriquez, Braylon Council, Hiparco Hernandez, Salvador Garcia, Mario Arias, Abdon Galindo and Carlos Soto.
